{"tid":1402743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前中後排新手老手立即同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:12:25.000Z","uid":14802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0edc4535efee479306a5b2ea372844283da45d25","tid":1402743,"uid":14802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"預咗俾人屌散水分化撚<br />\n<br />\n香城online幾個職都做過<br />\n個副本明明係限時內任玩 <br />\n夠鐘就出npc狂暴mode掃場封副本出口<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而個任務係不論新手老手都要安全通關走人</span></span><br />\n仲未計出到副本會有人開紅打新手<br />\n喺洪水路同十字路口放完麻痹陷阱就應該出副本<br />\n事前亦都同過前線講十字路口輸過太多次 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放完陷阱立即走</span></span><br />\n（當時已經講緊npc入咗副本<br />\n728副本已經好多手足俾gm封ac <br />\n唔好再失去任何新手老手喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋仲要一齊805三罷架</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你個閪下次邊個叫留低話放流料一個個捉出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8ab9821fa2a8750a84ed5dcc6c4fcbb69c906da7","tid":1402743,"uid":14802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊記副本任務內容呀各位手足</span></span>"}]}